WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.160
Welcome to the Learn AI in 2

00:00:02.160 --> 00:00:02.960
minutes.

00:00:03.080 --> 00:00:06.100
Quick concept, simple metaphor and zero jargon

00:00:06.100 --> 00:00:06.900
over

00:00:06.640 --> 00:00:07.440
load.

00:00:07.600 --> 00:00:09.040
You probably use GPT everyday,

00:00:09.360 --> 00:00:10.160
right?

00:00:09.880 --> 00:00:12.780
But what actually is large language

00:00:12.780 --> 00:00:13.580
model?

00:00:14.280 --> 00:00:16.379
Think of LLM like an autocomplete on

00:00:16.379 --> 00:00:17.179
steroids.

00:00:17.400 --> 00:00:19.400
You type a few words, your phone

00:00:19.400 --> 00:00:20.380
suggests the next

00:00:20.380 --> 00:00:21.180
one.

00:00:21.280 --> 00:00:23.420
And LLM does the same thing, but

00:00:23.420 --> 00:00:24.400
at a massive

00:00:24.400 --> 00:00:25.200
scale.

00:00:24.780 --> 00:00:27.100
It was trained on billions of words

00:00:27.100 --> 00:00:29.360
from books, articles and D

00:00:29.360 --> 00:00:30.160
-web.

00:00:30.060 --> 00:00:30.860
It learned

00:00:30.520 --> 00:00:31.320
patterns.

00:00:31.640 --> 00:00:33.320
Her words usually follow other

00:00:33.320 --> 00:00:34.120
words.

00:00:34.260 --> 00:00:35.820
So when you ask a question, it

00:00:35.820 --> 00:00:36.620
doesn't look up

00:00:36.420 --> 00:00:37.220
things.

00:00:37.160 --> 00:00:39.980
It predicts the most likely next word,

00:00:40.460 --> 00:00:42.480
then the next, and the next, and

00:00:42.480 --> 00:00:43.880
then it forms a full

00:00:43.880 --> 00:00:44.680
answer.

00:00:45.040 --> 00:00:46.240
It's not a search engine, to be

00:00:46.240 --> 00:00:47.040
honest.

00:00:46.680 --> 00:00:47.520
It's not a human brain

00:00:47.520 --> 00:00:48.320
either.

00:00:48.360 --> 00:00:49.680
It's a pattern prediction

00:00:49.680 --> 00:00:50.500
machine.

00:00:51.220 --> 00:00:52.860
And that's what makes it so

00:00:52.860 --> 00:00:53.660
powerful.

00:00:53.380 --> 00:00:56.960
So remember, an LLM predicts the most

00:00:56.960 --> 00:00:57.880
likely next

00:00:57.880 --> 00:00:58.680
words.

00:00:58.860 --> 00:01:00.980
These don't patterns, it learned from the

00:01:00.980 --> 00:01:01.780
text.

00:01:01.840 --> 00:01:03.300
Powerful, but not

00:01:03.300 --> 00:01:04.100
magic.

00:01:04.780 --> 00:01:05.820
That's your concept for

00:01:05.820 --> 00:01:06.620
today.

00:01:06.540 --> 00:01:07.340
Follow for the next

00:01:07.180 --> 00:01:07.980
one.

00:01:07.880 --> 00:01:09.060
Learn AI in 2

00:01:09.060 --> 00:01:09.860
minutes.

